WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.890
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.710
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.390 --> 02:49.910
[Episode 8]

02:51.190 --> 02:52.360
Master.

02:53.030 --> 02:54.680
I found the tomb of Qian Yin.

02:57.740 --> 02:59.540
I found that he died

02:59.570 --> 03:01.310
two days before my parents died.

03:02.400 --> 03:04.560
If my parents hadn't been killed by Qian Yin,

03:05.130 --> 03:07.200
they could still be alive, right?

03:07.220 --> 03:10.030
Back then, I went deep into the Demon Race to kill Qian Yin,

03:10.860 --> 03:13.180
only to learn he'd died in an internal power struggle.

03:13.210 --> 03:16.370
I didn't even find where he was buried.

03:16.390 --> 03:18.110
How did you find it?

03:18.140 --> 03:19.520
Fu Ling told me.

03:21.680 --> 03:23.210
Fu Ling from Cold Spring Palace?

03:24.060 --> 03:26.400
Why did you get involved with a demon?

03:27.160 --> 03:29.320
In Ning'an City, I thought she was a human.

03:29.340 --> 03:30.570
I saved her life, so…

03:30.600 --> 03:31.160
You fool!

03:32.000 --> 03:34.210
How can you believe what a demon said?

03:34.230 --> 03:36.280
Moreover, it's just a tombstone.

03:36.300 --> 03:37.350
She must be on

03:37.370 --> 03:38.730
something else.

03:39.280 --> 03:40.480
Chong Zhao,

03:40.750 --> 03:42.030
I know

03:42.060 --> 03:44.130
you've never gotten over

03:44.150 --> 03:45.640
your parents' deaths.

03:46.579 --> 03:48.650
But as a disciple of Lanling,

03:48.680 --> 03:49.730
you should know

03:50.410 --> 03:51.740
once the soul lamp goes out,

03:52.150 --> 03:53.980
there's no chance of living.

03:54.460 --> 03:56.460
It's irreversible.

03:57.020 --> 03:57.990
Besides,

03:58.020 --> 03:59.900
if they were still alive,

03:59.920 --> 04:01.200
why would they have left you

04:01.230 --> 04:03.230
and never come back?

04:05.010 --> 04:06.970
You should let it go.

04:10.890 --> 04:12.520
West sun mountain.

04:12.540 --> 04:14.170
East moon river.

04:14.200 --> 04:16.450
A snake slithers across the grass.

04:16.470 --> 04:18.760
A fish leaps above the sandy sea.

04:18.790 --> 04:21.000
The earth knows, but the sky does not.

04:21.019 --> 04:23.020
Only by stepping in can you find the way.

04:23.190 --> 04:25.420
This is a nursery rhyme from the Desireless Stone?

04:25.650 --> 04:27.260
I don't understand a single line of it.

04:27.290 --> 04:28.360
"West sun mountain"

04:28.380 --> 04:29.220
means the sun

04:29.250 --> 04:31.130
is about to set from the west of the mountain.

04:31.390 --> 04:32.350
"East moon river"

04:32.370 --> 04:33.140
means the moon

04:33.170 --> 04:35.180
is about to rise from the east of the sea.

04:35.810 --> 04:36.810
The sun and the moon

04:36.840 --> 04:38.060
are both visible at twilight.

04:38.870 --> 04:39.990
What unusual sights might appear

04:40.010 --> 04:41.250
in the desert at twilight?

04:41.920 --> 04:43.020
A mirage?

04:43.220 --> 04:44.420
That's what I thought too.

04:44.450 --> 04:45.940
If it's a mirage,

04:45.960 --> 04:47.590
then the snake and fish

04:47.620 --> 04:49.790
should be just illusions.

04:51.720 --> 04:54.200
What does it mean by a snake slithering across the grass?

04:55.380 --> 04:56.850
You don't live among humans,

04:56.880 --> 04:58.170
so you don't know about it.

04:58.190 --> 04:59.950
It's a riddle of the Human Race.

05:00.130 --> 05:01.820
A riddle?

05:01.850 --> 05:02.850
In the human culture,

05:02.870 --> 05:04.190
we have the zodiac.

05:04.220 --> 05:05.550
The snake in the zodiac

05:05.570 --> 05:07.570
corresponds to the "Si" in the Earthly Branches.

05:07.890 --> 05:10.400
A snake slithering across the grass means "Si" slithering across the grass.

05:11.630 --> 05:14.860
The character "Si," combined with the grass radical,

05:15.590 --> 05:16.960
becomes the character "Yi," as in Yi City.

05:17.160 --> 05:19.020
The Desireless Stone is telling me

05:19.040 --> 05:21.280
this nursery rhyme is the key to finding Yi City.

05:22.120 --> 05:22.890
Master,

05:22.910 --> 05:25.130
if only we knew better about the human culture.

05:28.120 --> 05:30.350
It's not surprising to find a snake in the desert,

05:30.580 --> 05:32.900
but how do we explain a fish leaping above the sandy sea?

05:32.980 --> 05:34.390
How could there be fish in the desert?

05:34.860 --> 05:36.340
I still haven't figured that out.

05:36.870 --> 05:37.670
Looks like

05:38.190 --> 05:39.630
we need to see this mirage

05:39.630 --> 05:41.070
for ourselves.

06:23.520 --> 06:25.320
Turns out it's the city walls blocking the view.

06:26.480 --> 06:28.480
People mistook the snake's tail for a fish's tail.

06:29.140 --> 06:30.380
Just looking at the tail,

06:30.400 --> 06:32.920
it looks like a giant fish leaping into the sandy sea.

06:32.950 --> 06:34.310
Then what do the last two lines mean?

06:34.330 --> 06:35.570
The earth knows, but the sky does not.

06:35.600 --> 06:37.240
Only by stepping in can you find the way.

06:39.030 --> 06:40.790
Maybe we can only find a clue

06:40.820 --> 06:42.040
by going to the mirage site.

06:48.020 --> 06:49.860
This is just the illusion of Yi City.

06:50.240 --> 06:52.440
Where is the real Yi City?

07:22.200 --> 07:23.160
What's wrong?

07:24.120 --> 07:25.770
I can't explain it, but it feels strange.

07:26.800 --> 07:28.390
Everything just seems too easy.

07:35.240 --> 07:36.290
Oh no!

07:36.790 --> 07:37.610
It's a sand formation!

07:47.840 --> 07:48.610
Don't let go.

07:50.970 --> 07:51.940
Hold on tight!

07:59.140 --> 07:59.950
Hold on tight.

08:06.560 --> 08:07.650
The suction is too strong.

08:07.670 --> 08:09.020
I can't hold on much longer!

08:09.050 --> 08:09.960
Don't worry.

08:10.320 --> 08:11.790
I won't let anything happen to you.

08:17.530 --> 08:21.810
♫No matter if I'm drunk or not, I just want to be reckless once♫

08:24.060 --> 08:29.390
♫Because love is thrilling♫

08:30.030 --> 08:33.530
♫If you tear open my heart♫

08:34.330 --> 08:36.640
♫I can hold you a little tighter♫

08:37.190 --> 08:41.510
♫This pain will gradually fade♫

08:43.789 --> 08:44.630
Bai Shuo.

08:44.250 --> 08:47.980
♫Time withers the moonlight♫

08:44.630 --> 08:47.440
A snake slithers across the grass.

08:47.440 --> 08:50.030
A fish leaps above the sandy sea.

08:48.320 --> 08:50.900
♫All that's left is pitch darkness♫

08:50.030 --> 08:52.720
The earth knows, but the sky does not.

08:51.200 --> 08:52.960
♫I want to tear apart♫

08:52.720 --> 08:55.600
Only by stepping in can you find the way.

08:53.990 --> 08:56.780
♫This sky for you♫

08:56.000 --> 08:56.600
Fan Yue.

08:56.600 --> 08:57.480
I understand.

08:57.570 --> 09:00.540
♫A lifetime of guarding everything with you♫

08:58.910 --> 08:59.670
Bai Shuo!

09:00.760 --> 09:04.230
♫Crossing the abyss to fulfill our vow♫

09:04.470 --> 09:07.880
♫I'll leap without a thought for tomorrow♫

09:08.150 --> 09:10.750
♫This moment feels like forever♫

09:10.860 --> 09:14.010
♫I've missed too much time in my life♫

09:14.320 --> 09:18.130
♫I'll throw myself into this flame for you♫

09:15.270 --> 09:16.720
Who allowed you to let go of my hand?

09:17.030 --> 09:17.790
It's because I found…

09:17.790 --> 09:18.600
I don't care!

09:18.330 --> 09:20.320
♫Even if I'll perish♫

09:19.200 --> 09:20.630
Do you know that one wrong judgment

09:20.370 --> 09:23.140
♫At least I can still kiss your face♫

09:20.630 --> 09:21.550
could cost you your life?

09:23.370 --> 09:27.130
♫Burn out my waning moon♫

09:24.440 --> 09:25.550
But you still followed me in.

09:26.550 --> 09:28.390
Did you trust my judgment,

09:27.390 --> 09:35.810
♫In exchange for a lifetime of passion♫

09:28.390 --> 09:29.510
or were you afraid I'd die?

09:30.320 --> 09:31.630
It's because I've said before

09:32.440 --> 09:33.530
that I won't let you die.

09:38.910 --> 09:39.670
Your arm.

09:41.120 --> 09:41.960
What are you going to do?

09:46.890 --> 09:51.380
♫No matter if I'm drunk or not, I just want to be reckless once♫

09:48.970 --> 09:49.770
I believe you.

09:51.080 --> 09:52.960
I believe you won't let me die.

09:52.980 --> 09:54.510
I always keep my word.

09:53.420 --> 09:58.940
♫Because love is thrilling♫

09:54.670 --> 09:55.790
Don't worry.

09:55.810 --> 09:57.520
I won't let myself die.

09:58.410 --> 10:00.530
Do you remember the last two lines of that rhyme?

09:59.390 --> 10:03.210
♫If you tear open my heart♫

10:00.560 --> 10:02.050
The earth knows, but the sky does not.

10:02.070 --> 10:03.650
Only by stepping in can you find the way.

10:03.670 --> 10:04.920
They hint that

10:03.690 --> 10:06.830
♫I can hold you a little tighter♫

10:04.950 --> 10:06.030
the answer is underground.

10:06.080 --> 10:07.550
Only if we go with the wind

10:07.000 --> 10:11.090
♫This pain will gradually fade♫

10:07.550 --> 10:09.400
to the underground

10:09.420 --> 10:11.300
can we find the entrance.

10:11.320 --> 10:13.390
That's still no reason for you to let go of my hand.

10:13.610 --> 10:17.480
♫Time withers the moonlight♫

10:14.270 --> 10:15.270
Your life

10:15.990 --> 10:17.020
is mine.

10:17.680 --> 10:20.260
♫All that's left is pitch darkness♫

10:18.640 --> 10:19.570
Fan Yue.

10:20.270 --> 10:22.280
Although you came down because of me,

10:20.330 --> 10:22.710
♫I want to tear apart♫

10:22.310 --> 10:24.140
I still have to correct you.

10:23.350 --> 10:26.270
♫This sky for you♫

10:24.640 --> 10:25.670
My life

10:25.700 --> 10:27.220
has always been my own.

10:27.270 --> 10:28.390
Thank you for following me,

10:28.390 --> 10:30.180
risking your life without hesitation.

10:30.200 --> 10:31.720
But without you,

10:31.750 --> 10:32.800
I'd still save myself.

10:36.040 --> 10:38.560
This must be the core of the sand formation.

10:38.710 --> 10:39.550
I feel

10:39.580 --> 10:41.030
the entrance to the city is right here.

10:43.600 --> 10:44.360
Hold on to me.

10:46.010 --> 10:47.290
Hold on to my sleeve.

10:52.900 --> 10:53.900
Stick close to me.

10:53.930 --> 10:55.620
Don't go anywhere or act rashly.

10:56.270 --> 10:57.630
There may be other formations.

11:25.570 --> 11:28.350
[Hua Lin, King of Yi]

11:33.270 --> 11:35.630
I didn't expect the Master of Bright Moon Palace to visit.

11:35.650 --> 11:37.290
I apologize for not welcoming you properly.

11:38.300 --> 11:39.780
Yi City has been locked down for seven years,

11:40.220 --> 11:41.790
yet you recognize me.

11:41.820 --> 11:43.100
Seven years of locking the city

11:43.120 --> 11:44.670
doesn't mean we're out of touch with the world.

11:44.700 --> 11:46.940
You're famous far and wide.

11:46.960 --> 11:48.080
I've long

11:48.110 --> 11:49.350
heard of your name.

11:49.370 --> 11:50.670
In that case,

11:50.770 --> 11:52.400
that sand formation earlier

11:52.430 --> 11:54.240
was your way of welcoming me?

11:54.570 --> 11:56.020
Yi City has been oppressed

11:56.120 --> 11:58.310
by Eternals and demons for a thousand years.

11:58.490 --> 11:59.540
The sand formation

12:00.020 --> 12:01.990
is just for defensive purposes.

12:03.260 --> 12:04.260
This young lady

12:04.290 --> 12:06.090
is very smart.

12:06.120 --> 12:07.600
Your courage is commendable.

12:07.620 --> 12:09.110
In the face of life and death,

12:09.140 --> 12:10.680
you remained calm

12:11.050 --> 12:12.590
and saw through the pattern of the formation.

12:13.180 --> 12:15.300
I must say, I'm impressed.

12:15.320 --> 12:17.670
I'm not particularly smart or wise,

12:17.700 --> 12:19.060
and I'm not fearless either.

12:19.610 --> 12:20.700
I just know

12:20.720 --> 12:22.730
there's another way to live in this world.

12:22.750 --> 12:24.590
It's called "live after death."

12:24.680 --> 12:25.720
No wonder Master Fan Yue

12:25.750 --> 12:27.840
risked his own life to save you.

12:28.510 --> 12:30.010
I've come here to tell you

12:30.180 --> 12:31.700
that within three days,

12:31.730 --> 12:33.030
you should send invitations

12:33.110 --> 12:34.950
to all Eternals and demons

12:35.340 --> 12:36.940
for the Wutong Martial Arts Contest.

12:38.330 --> 12:39.270
Why?

12:39.290 --> 12:40.770
You should know

12:41.490 --> 12:42.520
Bright Moon Palace

12:42.540 --> 12:44.560
is a place no one dares to trespass in the Polar Region.

12:44.580 --> 12:46.240
King of Yi, if you agree,

12:46.360 --> 12:48.570
I'll allow Yi City to move into the Polar Region

12:48.590 --> 12:49.500
under my protection.

12:49.900 --> 12:51.060
But if not,

12:51.640 --> 12:53.000
I doubt you have time

12:53.020 --> 12:54.990
to move the city within three days.

12:57.300 --> 12:57.970
The easy way

12:58.570 --> 12:59.420
and the hard one

12:59.900 --> 13:00.810
are both in front of you.

13:01.210 --> 13:02.930
You choose.

13:06.750 --> 13:07.820
Your Majesty,

13:08.010 --> 13:08.650
back then,

13:08.680 --> 13:09.560
the first King of Yi

13:09.580 --> 13:11.580
agreed to host the Wutong Martial Arts Contest

13:11.610 --> 13:13.450
to earn the respect of Eternals and demons

13:13.470 --> 13:14.910
for peaceful coexistence.

13:14.930 --> 13:16.450
We've held the Contest for a thousand years

13:16.480 --> 13:17.570
and put in a lot of effort,

13:17.600 --> 13:19.690
but they still look down on us.

13:19.710 --> 13:21.140
If we hold the Contest again,

13:21.170 --> 13:22.290
the people in the city

13:21.630 --> 13:23.540
[Wu Zhao, Deputy General of Yi City]

13:22.310 --> 13:23.620
will complain more.

13:24.090 --> 13:25.850
Although the protection

13:25.880 --> 13:27.070
the Master of Bright Moon Palace

13:27.090 --> 13:29.180
offers seems tempting,

13:29.900 --> 13:31.140
we don't truly know

13:31.260 --> 13:32.900
his real intentions.

13:33.410 --> 13:34.760
We must not trust him so easily.

13:36.700 --> 13:38.220
I know that.

13:38.480 --> 13:40.270
But now, Yi City is exposed.

13:41.050 --> 13:42.620
Moving the city in three days

13:42.640 --> 13:43.720
is simply impossible.

13:44.370 --> 13:45.800
If the Eternals and demons

13:45.820 --> 13:47.390
discover Yi City's location,

13:47.560 --> 13:49.010
the secrets of the city

13:49.040 --> 13:50.550
can no longer be hidden.

13:50.620 --> 13:51.830
Whether I agree or not,

13:52.570 --> 13:53.650
it will be troublesome.

13:55.200 --> 13:56.560
King of Yi.

14:15.710 --> 14:16.850
Zhen Yu?

14:17.250 --> 14:18.490
Long time no see.

14:18.920 --> 14:20.880
Is this how you welcome your guests?

14:25.500 --> 14:26.460
Zhen Yu.

14:26.970 --> 14:28.700
How did you find this place?

14:29.120 --> 14:30.070
Was it difficult?

14:30.090 --> 14:31.810
If Fan Yue could find it,

14:31.840 --> 14:33.050
it would be

14:33.710 --> 14:35.380
a piece of cake for me.

14:35.410 --> 14:36.840
What do you want?

14:37.660 --> 14:38.940
Why are you so vigilant?

14:41.330 --> 14:43.020
I came here today

14:43.090 --> 14:45.050
to help Yi City.

14:45.570 --> 14:46.760
I can help you keep the secrets

14:46.780 --> 14:48.310
you wish to keep

14:48.890 --> 14:50.250
and solve

14:50.280 --> 14:51.190
the problems

14:51.650 --> 14:53.580
you want to solve.

14:54.040 --> 14:55.170
Every deal

14:55.200 --> 14:56.470
has its price.

14:56.490 --> 14:57.770
What do you want?

14:57.800 --> 14:58.610
Straight to the point.

14:59.110 --> 15:00.330
You must have heard of

15:00.820 --> 15:02.220
the Desireless Stone.

15:07.680 --> 15:08.600
Sect Leader,

15:08.620 --> 15:10.670
are we about to attack Bright Moon Palace?

15:10.700 --> 15:12.540
I've decided on the moves. Look.

15:19.400 --> 15:20.760
Calm down.

15:20.790 --> 15:21.710
Sit down first.

15:22.110 --> 15:22.710
Alright.

15:24.750 --> 15:25.600
Today,

15:25.600 --> 15:29.030
I've gathered everyone here to discuss another matter.

15:29.030 --> 15:31.230
King of Yi has sent an invitation.

15:31.260 --> 15:32.930
He's invited all Eternals and demons

15:32.950 --> 15:34.640
to go to Yi City

15:34.110 --> 15:36.730
[and strengthen the bonds between the three races. We invite the esteemed guests of Lanling to join us in Yi City.]

15:34.110 --> 15:36.730
[On the 15th of this month, the Wutong Martial Arts Contest will be held to test the abilities of Eternals and demons]

15:34.670 --> 15:36.700
for the Wutong Martial Arts Contest.

15:37.620 --> 15:38.980
He wants to ease

15:38.540 --> 15:41.230
[and strengthen the bonds between the three races. We invite the esteemed guests of Lanling to join us in Yi City.]

15:38.540 --> 15:41.230
[On the 15th of this month, the Wutong Martial Arts Contest will be held to test the abilities of Eternals and demons]

15:39.030 --> 15:42.510
the relationship between the Yi citizens and the two races.

15:42.510 --> 15:45.050
The Contest hasn't been held for seven years.

15:45.210 --> 15:46.920
They just hold it and cancel it

15:46.950 --> 15:48.920
as they please.

15:48.950 --> 15:50.750
Are we fools in their eyes?

15:50.780 --> 15:51.780
I won't go!

15:51.800 --> 15:52.760
That's right.

15:52.780 --> 15:55.340
Seven years ago, King of Yi suddenly canceled the Contest,

15:55.720 --> 15:58.190
which led to more fighting between the Eternals and demons.

15:58.510 --> 15:59.960
If Eternals enter Yi City,

15:59.960 --> 16:01.640
they'll surely get into fights with demons.

16:01.800 --> 16:03.130
Lanling

16:03.160 --> 16:04.640
doesn't need to get into that mess.

16:04.670 --> 16:06.590
Don't rush to object.

16:06.610 --> 16:08.720
Let me finish.

16:08.740 --> 16:10.020
The winner of the Contest

16:10.050 --> 16:12.140
will get the Wutong Spirit Pill.

16:13.800 --> 16:15.230
How could I forget that?

16:15.670 --> 16:16.840
If that's the case,

16:16.860 --> 16:18.570
maybe we should reconsider.

16:18.940 --> 16:21.100
The Wutong Spirit Pill is a rare spiritual treasure.

16:21.130 --> 16:23.160
It can greatly enhance cultivation.

16:23.540 --> 16:25.300
Even if we don't need it,

16:25.320 --> 16:26.770
we can sell it to other Eternal sects.

16:26.800 --> 16:28.400
It'd be enough to support us for three years.

16:28.440 --> 16:29.250
Three years?

16:29.280 --> 16:31.050
It would last us ten years!

16:31.500 --> 16:34.020
Since no one has any objections,

16:34.040 --> 16:35.210
then

16:35.240 --> 16:37.180
Chong Zhao will lead the team.

16:37.200 --> 16:38.480
Yes, Master.

16:38.510 --> 16:39.470
But...

16:39.600 --> 16:40.690
Don't worry,

16:41.270 --> 16:44.230
I haven't forgotten about the Desireless Stone.

16:44.640 --> 16:46.090
The Contest this time

16:46.120 --> 16:48.200
is not only for the Eternals.

16:48.220 --> 16:50.570
Bright Moon Palace, Jingyou Mountain, and other demon clans

16:50.600 --> 16:52.690
are also invited.

16:52.710 --> 16:54.730
Bai Shuo, eager to grow stronger,

16:54.760 --> 16:56.550
will likely attend it as well.

16:56.960 --> 16:59.810
We can wait for her in Yi City

17:00.540 --> 17:02.740
instead of searching for her in the Polar Region.

17:02.760 --> 17:04.160
Isn't that much easier?

17:04.190 --> 17:05.230
Then I'll go!

17:05.250 --> 17:07.250
Calm down.

17:07.640 --> 17:09.680
Yi City has a restriction formation.

17:09.700 --> 17:12.030
Even the strongest Eternals and demons

17:12.060 --> 17:13.490
can't use their magic there.

17:13.510 --> 17:15.510
They can only rely on physical strength.

17:15.540 --> 17:18.260
So whether you go or Chong Zhao goes,

17:18.280 --> 17:19.690
it makes no difference.

17:22.720 --> 17:23.839
Chong Zhao,

17:23.859 --> 17:25.130
the Wutong Contest

17:25.160 --> 17:27.440
is not just a simple martial arts competition.

17:27.810 --> 17:29.050
It's a comprehensive test

17:29.080 --> 17:32.000
of strength, intelligence,

17:32.030 --> 17:34.510
temperament, and character.

17:35.030 --> 17:37.030
So, going to Yi City

17:37.060 --> 17:38.380
will certainly be dangerous.

17:39.020 --> 17:40.310
Remember,

17:40.460 --> 17:42.610
bringing Bai Shuo back is secondary.

17:42.630 --> 17:45.480
The most important thing is to protect your fellow disciples.

17:45.950 --> 17:46.990
Understood, Master.

17:52.500 --> 17:54.990
This is my Cangxuan Sword.

17:55.520 --> 17:57.080
It has a century-old sword spirit

17:57.100 --> 17:59.180
and will be useful at a crucial moment.

17:59.570 --> 18:00.760
Thank you, Master.

18:01.410 --> 18:03.000
I never said I was giving it to you.

18:06.210 --> 18:07.290
But if it's useful,

18:07.320 --> 18:09.140
then take it.

18:10.770 --> 18:11.760
Thank you, Master.

18:16.640 --> 18:19.900
[and strengthen the bonds between the three races. We invite the esteemed guests of Lanling to join us in Yi City.]

18:16.640 --> 18:19.900
[On the 15th of this month, the Wutong Martial Arts Contest will be held to test the abilities of Eternals and demons]

18:19.540 --> 18:21.500
King of Yi knows how to read the room.

18:21.520 --> 18:22.560
Knowing there's no escape,

18:22.590 --> 18:24.030
he's agreed to hold the Contest.

18:24.580 --> 18:26.160
King of Yi is shrewd

18:26.160 --> 18:27.720
and has always despised Eternals and demons.

18:27.720 --> 18:29.750
Master has figured out Yi City's location,

18:30.140 --> 18:32.140
but he's agreed to our terms too easily.

18:32.170 --> 18:34.180
Once the city gates are open,

18:34.200 --> 18:35.950
whether it's a conspiracy or something else,

18:36.830 --> 18:38.620
I'll be right there to see it through.

18:46.410 --> 18:47.300
Grand Master,

18:47.730 --> 18:49.510
King of Yi has already sent out invitations

18:49.510 --> 18:51.370
to all Eternals and demons for the Wutong Contest.

18:51.390 --> 18:52.910
When there's more fish than food,

18:52.940 --> 18:54.310
we've got to fight

18:54.330 --> 18:55.370
to get what we want.

18:56.400 --> 18:58.090
Yi City reopening

18:58.120 --> 18:59.470
only means it's all but over.

19:00.710 --> 19:02.360
Even if they fight to the death,

19:02.380 --> 19:04.160
what difference will it make?

19:04.180 --> 19:05.510
In the end,

19:05.550 --> 19:08.180
they'll all fall into my hands.

19:08.210 --> 19:09.170
But...

19:09.980 --> 19:11.620
they'll all be dead by then.

19:16.160 --> 19:21.050
[Yi City, home to Yi citizens]

19:28.960 --> 19:30.470
Who are they?

19:45.200 --> 19:47.270
Alright, alright, alright.

19:47.300 --> 19:48.270
No more fooling around!

19:48.270 --> 19:48.960
Go home!

19:48.960 --> 19:50.960
I'll teach you a lesson after we get back!

20:00.590 --> 20:02.480
This is Yi City, huh?

20:02.500 --> 20:04.090
It really looks different.

20:04.190 --> 20:05.400
These Yi citizens

20:05.420 --> 20:06.940
are surprisingly

20:06.970 --> 20:07.930
strong.

20:20.790 --> 20:22.930
They don't seem to welcome us.

20:22.950 --> 20:25.710
Yi citizens have been at loggerheads with Eternals and demons for over 1,000 years.

20:26.180 --> 20:27.570
Eternals and demons look down on them,

20:28.160 --> 20:28.880
and they despise

20:28.910 --> 20:30.310
Eternals and demons.

20:31.810 --> 20:32.880
When we're in Yi City,

20:32.880 --> 20:34.550
don't leave my sight.

20:37.480 --> 20:39.180
If you die, the Desireless Stone will be useless.

20:40.880 --> 20:42.600
Just take care of yourself.

20:42.620 --> 20:43.470
The city gates have opened.

20:43.500 --> 20:44.970
The Eternals will arrive soon.

20:45.070 --> 20:46.640
You took their Desireless Stone.

20:46.640 --> 20:48.000
They can't wait to kill you.

20:49.100 --> 20:50.610
The Eternals will come, so what?

20:50.640 --> 20:52.130
Their power will be restricted too.

20:52.150 --> 20:53.310
Even if it wasn't,

20:53.340 --> 20:54.030
Bright Moon Palace

20:54.050 --> 20:55.470
wouldn't be afraid of those Eternals.

20:55.500 --> 20:56.660
Restricted?

20:56.870 --> 20:58.030
In Yi City,

20:58.060 --> 20:59.820
Eternals and demons can't use their magic.

20:59.850 --> 21:01.470
Then why the Contest?

21:01.550 --> 21:03.090
With punches, kicks, swords,

21:03.240 --> 21:04.040
and clubs,

21:04.570 --> 21:05.530
we can still fight.

21:06.740 --> 21:08.650
So in Yi City,

21:08.680 --> 21:10.940
one can only rely on weapons and physical strength.

21:11.960 --> 21:13.720
Neither Eternals nor demons can use magic.

21:13.790 --> 21:15.890
That gives me a better chance of winning.

21:16.730 --> 21:18.180
Stop dreaming.

21:18.340 --> 21:19.710
Even without magic,

21:19.740 --> 21:20.970
I can still easily

21:20.990 --> 21:22.150
hold you in my palm.

21:23.650 --> 21:24.940
You're overthinking it.

21:28.500 --> 21:29.370
Shuo.

21:35.090 --> 21:36.090
Why are you here?

21:36.920 --> 21:38.720
She's with Bright Moon Palace.

21:38.740 --> 21:39.800
Where she is

21:40.000 --> 21:41.110
is none of your business.

21:41.850 --> 21:42.830
Shuo.

21:42.890 --> 21:44.460
You shouldn't stay with demons,

21:44.490 --> 21:46.040
and you shouldn't have come here.

21:46.700 --> 21:47.950
Who I stay with

21:47.970 --> 21:49.010
and where I go

21:49.450 --> 21:50.690
are my decisions to make.

21:50.710 --> 21:52.190
Demons can't be trusted.

21:54.940 --> 21:56.300
We're not here to fight.

21:57.470 --> 21:58.250
We?

21:59.780 --> 22:01.130
Since there's a "we,"

22:01.160 --> 22:02.290
don't pick the wrong side.

22:02.770 --> 22:04.080
Think carefully about

22:04.100 --> 22:05.300
who you should trust

22:05.330 --> 22:06.410
and who you should choose.

22:10.640 --> 22:12.350
I have my own plans.

22:13.050 --> 22:14.680
The Eternals can't give me what I want.

22:15.200 --> 22:16.750
We're destined to be on different paths.

22:19.020 --> 22:19.740
Let's go.

22:26.750 --> 22:27.550
Great!

22:28.240 --> 22:29.290
All the Eternals and demons

22:29.310 --> 22:30.590
have fallen into the trap.

22:30.620 --> 22:31.600
Everyone who needs to be there

22:31.620 --> 22:32.860
has already arrived.

22:32.890 --> 22:34.850
The grand Wutong Martial Arts Contest

22:34.870 --> 22:36.110
wouldn't be complete without

22:36.140 --> 22:37.420
us from Cold Spring Palace.

22:39.100 --> 22:39.930
Fu Ling.

22:41.310 --> 22:42.440
Go to Yi City

22:42.670 --> 22:44.300
and carry out the plan.

22:44.330 --> 22:45.300
Remember,

22:45.320 --> 22:46.760
keep a close eye on Bai Shuo.

22:46.790 --> 22:48.420
She must not

22:48.440 --> 22:49.770
leave Yi City.

22:49.800 --> 22:50.750
Understood.

22:57.200 --> 22:58.130
Grand Master.

22:58.310 --> 22:59.810
Why send Fu Ling?

22:59.850 --> 23:02.060
Aren't you worried that Chong Zhao could mess things up

23:02.100 --> 23:03.470
and ruin your plan?

23:04.360 --> 23:06.160
No plan can be foolproof.

23:06.180 --> 23:08.580
I just need to have backup plans.

23:09.090 --> 23:10.440
In Yi City,

23:10.460 --> 23:12.300
you've got other people in place?

23:12.330 --> 23:13.570
People are simple.

23:13.590 --> 23:15.030
As long as they're properly used,

23:15.060 --> 23:15.650
anyone

23:15.670 --> 23:18.030
can become my pawn.

23:35.720 --> 23:38.200
[Sihai Inn]

23:55.310 --> 23:56.310
Come on.

23:56.310 --> 23:57.720
Bring it on!

24:00.590 --> 24:02.000
I'll teach you a hard lesson!

24:03.810 --> 24:05.560
Bring it on! You want the room?

24:05.580 --> 24:06.710
Who do you think you are?

24:06.740 --> 24:07.610
Exactly.

24:08.780 --> 24:10.150
Demon, you're dead!

24:10.540 --> 24:12.830
How dare you act up in front of me?

24:28.390 --> 24:29.280
You good?

24:30.280 --> 24:31.480
Stop fighting.

24:35.780 --> 24:37.210
I'm not afraid of you. Bring it on!

24:53.390 --> 24:54.550
Looks like

24:54.580 --> 24:56.890
the prophecy from the Desireless Stone has come true again.

24:56.920 --> 24:58.750
Could this Contemplation

24:58.770 --> 25:00.310
be related to the conflict between the two races?

25:07.290 --> 25:09.330
[Nan Wan, Eternal Race, Yunxiao Sect]

25:07.410 --> 25:09.060
That's my room!

25:11.320 --> 25:14.110
-Enough. Calm down.
-You deserve a good beating!

25:14.340 --> 25:15.490
You want to die?

25:15.520 --> 25:16.650
-Bring it on!
-What are you talking about?

25:17.460 --> 25:18.460
Everyone.

25:19.490 --> 25:21.400
The top-tier rooms

25:21.420 --> 25:23.550
should naturally be the Eternals'.

25:23.580 --> 25:24.860
Look at you,

25:24.880 --> 25:26.240
a bunch of furry beasts,

25:26.270 --> 25:28.030
wandering around like street rats.

25:26.370 --> 25:27.680
[Xiao Kan, Demon Race, a wolf demon]

25:28.110 --> 25:30.030
Second-tier rooms suit you the best, unless…

25:30.770 --> 25:31.720
you prefer the bathrooms.

25:31.750 --> 25:32.880
What are you saying?

25:34.180 --> 25:35.220
Listen up!

25:35.240 --> 25:36.440
I'm talking about you guys,

25:37.020 --> 25:38.220
a bunch of stinky foxes.

25:38.670 --> 25:39.680
Bei Chen.

25:39.290 --> 25:40.530
[Bei Chen, Eternal Race, Kunlun Sect]

25:40.030 --> 25:41.430
Say something!

25:42.110 --> 25:43.220
Aren't Kunlun

25:43.250 --> 25:45.400
and the Fox Clan sworn enemies?

25:45.420 --> 25:46.380
Why are you

25:46.920 --> 25:47.810
so quiet today?

25:53.740 --> 25:54.590
Let me say something.

25:54.590 --> 25:55.400
Stop.

25:55.420 --> 25:56.920
I insist.

25:56.950 --> 25:58.410
We Eternals believe that

25:58.440 --> 26:00.520
from one breath, three purities are born.

26:00.770 --> 26:01.680
As…

26:02.480 --> 26:05.440
As Eternals, we should restrain our evil desires,

26:05.460 --> 26:07.180
clear out the bad energy,

26:07.570 --> 26:09.260
and make it pure again.

26:09.280 --> 26:10.350
My Eternal friends,

26:10.400 --> 26:11.960
stop arguing.

26:11.990 --> 26:12.470
Come on.

26:12.490 --> 26:13.900
Let's recite

26:13.930 --> 26:16.030
the Scripture of Forgetting Emotions.

26:16.970 --> 26:18.340
-Forgetting emotions…
-Shut up!

26:18.370 --> 26:20.490
I can't stand you Eternals and your scriptures!

26:20.550 --> 26:21.270
All you do

26:21.270 --> 26:22.110
is waste time!

26:22.110 --> 26:23.200
-Exactly.
-You…

26:27.170 --> 26:29.920
We're all here for the Wutong Martial Arts Contest,

26:29.950 --> 26:31.920
so why fight over something pointless?

26:31.940 --> 26:32.770
Bah!

26:32.830 --> 26:33.580
The Eternals from Kunlun

26:33.600 --> 26:34.750
are the most hypocritical.

26:34.780 --> 26:35.430
You guys

26:35.480 --> 26:36.160
are cruel and bloodthirsty.

26:36.160 --> 26:38.070
Since Eternals and demons can't get along,

26:38.070 --> 26:40.350
why do they have to stay in the same inn?

26:41.390 --> 26:43.070
It's the tradition of the Contest.

26:43.090 --> 26:45.710
The former King of Yi wanted to help the three races reconcile

26:45.730 --> 26:47.820
and set the rules with the heads of the other two races

26:47.850 --> 26:49.930
for Eternals, demons, and Yi citizens to stay together.

26:50.420 --> 26:52.260
But I think this rule is just for show.

26:52.280 --> 26:53.410
Once sides are taken,

26:53.440 --> 26:54.700
right or wrong doesn't matter,

26:54.730 --> 26:56.170
and the fighting never ends.

26:56.190 --> 26:57.120
Nonsense!

26:57.150 --> 26:58.060
It's your Saintess…

26:58.110 --> 26:59.350
Eternals and demons

26:59.350 --> 27:00.640
are not nobler than one another.

27:02.470 --> 27:04.050
You can't insult the Saint!

27:04.920 --> 27:07.120
Everyone, stop arguing!

27:08.490 --> 27:10.370
What's the point of fighting over the rooms?

27:11.260 --> 27:12.980
Lanling has old ties with many sects.

27:13.010 --> 27:14.620
Please listen to me.

27:14.690 --> 27:16.220
Look who's here.

27:16.860 --> 27:18.170
Isn't that

27:18.200 --> 27:20.510
Chong Zhao, the Eternal who couldn't even

27:20.870 --> 27:22.260
guard Ning'an City?

27:22.550 --> 27:24.180
They call you the head disciple of Lanling.

27:26.120 --> 27:27.440
But you're weak and incompetent,

27:27.460 --> 27:29.330
causing chaos in the whole city.

27:29.350 --> 27:30.550
If I were you,

27:30.580 --> 27:32.850
I'd have already buried myself in a hole.

27:32.880 --> 27:34.150
You don't deserve to come here

27:34.170 --> 27:35.900
and fight with us for the Wutong Spirit Pill.

27:35.930 --> 27:36.520
Nan Wan!

27:36.540 --> 27:37.620
That's nonsense!

27:37.640 --> 27:38.960
If Chong Zhao doesn't deserve to be here,

27:38.980 --> 27:40.430
then do you?

27:43.950 --> 27:45.870
You guys are Eternals,

27:45.960 --> 27:47.850
but instead of protecting the people,

27:47.870 --> 27:49.350
you're here fighting

27:49.380 --> 27:50.370
and arguing.

27:50.400 --> 27:51.880
Is that what Eternals do?

27:52.990 --> 27:54.900
You're just a human.

27:55.630 --> 27:57.350
How dare you lecture me?

28:00.550 --> 28:01.440
You're dead!

28:10.440 --> 28:11.110
Senior!

28:14.460 --> 28:15.260
Senior.

28:21.440 --> 28:23.520
You know where to seek protection, don't you?

28:26.990 --> 28:28.430
With someone like you around,

28:28.450 --> 28:29.540
if I don't make use of it,

28:29.570 --> 28:30.890
it'd be an ungodly waste.

28:34.220 --> 28:35.180
Are you alright?

28:35.490 --> 28:36.480
Senior.

28:36.920 --> 28:38.150
Who are you?

28:38.180 --> 28:39.580
Tell me your name!

28:40.070 --> 28:40.990
Forgot to mention.

28:41.680 --> 28:42.940
The top-tier rooms

28:43.480 --> 28:44.830
are all mine.

28:44.850 --> 28:45.790
Who do you think you are?

28:45.810 --> 28:46.960
Senior, calm down.

28:46.990 --> 28:48.160
He's so powerful.

28:48.200 --> 28:48.960
Forget it.

28:48.960 --> 28:50.230
The second-tier rooms will do too.

28:50.860 --> 28:51.830
Forget it.

29:06.340 --> 29:07.180
Why are you laughing?

29:08.630 --> 29:09.490
Nothing.

29:09.960 --> 29:11.200
It just feels good to boss around

29:11.200 --> 29:13.110
under your wings.

29:13.130 --> 29:14.310
I'll do it more often.

29:14.860 --> 29:16.900
Not anyone can stay by my side.

29:19.810 --> 29:23.070
Kill them! Kill them!

29:23.570 --> 29:24.440
Go!

29:24.470 --> 29:28.040
Kill them! Kill them!

29:30.090 --> 29:33.390
Kill them! Kill them!

29:33.410 --> 29:36.390
Kill them! Kill them!

29:36.410 --> 29:39.200
Kill them! Kill them!

29:39.230 --> 29:40.670
Kill those Eternals and demons!

29:40.690 --> 29:41.780
Yes, kill them!

29:41.810 --> 29:42.910
Kill them!

29:44.360 --> 29:45.080
Hey, bro,

29:45.100 --> 29:46.090
what are you...

29:46.120 --> 29:46.520
Bah!

29:46.730 --> 29:48.010
Don't call me bro.

29:48.040 --> 29:48.990
Eternals, demons—

29:49.010 --> 29:50.340
none of you guys are any good.

29:50.100 --> 29:51.720
[Hu's mother, a Yi citizen]

29:50.370 --> 29:51.370
You brought this disease

29:51.390 --> 29:52.950
into the city.

29:53.000 --> 29:54.110
You all deserve to die!

29:54.110 --> 29:55.000
Kill them!

29:55.000 --> 29:58.000
Kill them! Kill them! Kill them!

29:58.000 --> 29:58.830
Disease?

30:00.310 --> 30:01.510
[Hu, a Yi citizen]

30:02.170 --> 30:03.100
Chong Zhao.

30:03.130 --> 30:04.410
What's wrong with this kid?

30:04.720 --> 30:06.540
It doesn't look like an ordinary illness.

30:06.570 --> 30:07.790
Cut the crap!

30:08.440 --> 30:09.880
These Eternals and demons

30:09.910 --> 30:12.050
never cared about the lives of Yi citizens.

30:12.420 --> 30:13.830
If we kill them,

30:13.850 --> 30:14.920
the kid can be saved!

30:14.950 --> 30:16.800
Right, kill them! Kill them!

30:16.820 --> 30:18.240
Please, calm down.

30:18.480 --> 30:19.530
Enough.

30:20.200 --> 30:21.090
Yi citizens

30:22.010 --> 30:23.250
are all lowlifes.

30:23.280 --> 30:24.750
How dare you talk like that?

30:25.480 --> 30:26.700
Their king

30:26.750 --> 30:28.980
invited us to the Contest.

30:29.140 --> 30:30.940
Not only did they fail to host us properly,

30:30.960 --> 30:32.240
but now they're actually

30:32.270 --> 30:33.800
messing with us.

30:34.320 --> 30:35.190
Fine.

30:36.090 --> 30:37.200
Bring it on.

30:37.600 --> 30:38.810
I'd like to see

30:38.840 --> 30:40.320
what you can do

30:40.340 --> 30:41.320
with us today!

30:41.480 --> 30:42.510
Watch your mouth!

30:42.510 --> 30:44.200
Come on. Bring it on!

30:44.200 --> 30:44.790
We'll kill you all!

30:44.790 --> 30:47.040
I'm actually with him on this one.

30:47.200 --> 30:48.820
I was just getting started.

30:49.570 --> 30:51.570
I can't wait to see which one of you has a death wish

30:51.590 --> 30:52.910
and wants to try your luck with me.

30:52.940 --> 30:55.410
Come on!

30:56.340 --> 30:57.960
Hu.

30:57.980 --> 30:58.740
Hu.

31:00.880 --> 31:02.770
Hu, wake up!

31:02.790 --> 31:03.590
Hu!

31:05.100 --> 31:06.230
Listen.

31:06.260 --> 31:07.700
Take her away.

31:07.720 --> 31:08.840
If she dies here,

31:08.870 --> 31:09.930
we can't stay in this inn anymore.

31:13.370 --> 31:15.090
The situation is not clear yet.

31:15.430 --> 31:16.910
It's no good for you to be kind now.

31:19.480 --> 31:20.550
Hu.

31:21.480 --> 31:22.420
Hu!

31:22.460 --> 31:23.500
Kunlun is skilled in medicine.

31:23.530 --> 31:24.790
Do you know how to treat him?

31:25.190 --> 31:26.970
I've never seen a disease like this before.

31:26.990 --> 31:28.140
Why are you still there?

31:28.170 --> 31:29.340
Take her away!

31:29.360 --> 31:30.710
Don't bring bad luck to us.

31:30.740 --> 31:32.020
I knew it.

31:32.110 --> 31:33.930
None of you Eternals and demons are any good.

31:33.960 --> 31:35.000
Get out!

31:35.020 --> 31:39.150
Get out! Get out!

31:42.170 --> 31:42.970
Hu.

31:43.880 --> 31:44.910
Hu.

31:45.530 --> 31:47.320
Hu, hang in there!

31:47.830 --> 31:49.030
Hu.

31:50.110 --> 31:51.400
Hu.

31:51.400 --> 31:52.720
Don't sleep.

31:52.880 --> 31:54.750
Don't sleep!

31:55.110 --> 31:56.500
Hu, wake up!

31:56.520 --> 31:57.750
Hu, wake up!

31:57.750 --> 31:59.750
Hang in there!

32:02.770 --> 32:03.660
Hu.

32:03.680 --> 32:05.390
Hu, wake up!

32:05.410 --> 32:07.590
Hu, don't sleep.

32:07.620 --> 32:09.030
Hu!

32:09.130 --> 32:11.110
Wake up, Hu!

32:15.680 --> 32:17.340
What's that?

32:17.480 --> 32:18.530
I'm a human,

32:18.550 --> 32:19.870
not an Eternal or a demon.

32:19.900 --> 32:21.070
This pill can save her.

32:21.090 --> 32:22.620
Even if you're a human,

32:22.670 --> 32:24.420
you came here with Eternals and demons,

32:24.440 --> 32:26.410
so you're definitely with them.

32:29.870 --> 32:31.270
You can believe me or not.

32:31.550 --> 32:32.880
For me,

32:32.880 --> 32:34.040
whether I save her or not,

32:34.060 --> 32:35.300
it's no loss either way.

32:35.330 --> 32:36.570
What's more important,

32:36.590 --> 32:38.500
your child's life or hatred?

32:38.530 --> 32:39.820
You choose.

33:20.470 --> 33:22.050
Mom.

33:22.080 --> 33:24.630
-It worked.
-She's awake.

33:25.020 --> 33:26.140
Hu.

33:28.510 --> 33:29.370
Bai Shuo

33:29.400 --> 33:30.950
did learn something from Old Turtle.

33:30.970 --> 33:32.460
Her pills are great,

33:32.480 --> 33:33.890
but she's still

33:33.920 --> 33:35.010
too soft-hearted.

33:35.160 --> 33:36.050
Thanks

33:36.650 --> 33:37.570
for the pill.

33:38.140 --> 33:38.970
Earlier,

33:39.230 --> 33:40.400
I was wrong about you.

33:40.560 --> 33:41.590
It's fine.

33:41.620 --> 33:42.590
I don't care.

33:42.620 --> 33:44.220
Take her home for some rest.

33:49.900 --> 33:50.980
Look.

33:52.220 --> 33:54.980
Heart flame. That's the heart flame.

33:57.680 --> 33:59.750
The first heart flame has appeared.

34:05.740 --> 34:07.250
I've never seen one before.

34:11.300 --> 34:13.070
Why did it appear?

34:13.840 --> 34:16.239
Why is it landing on her?

34:21.219 --> 34:22.810
Why is it landing on her?

34:22.830 --> 34:24.380
-Yeah.
-Why?

34:26.929 --> 34:27.659
Wait.

34:27.679 --> 34:28.650
What are you doing?

34:28.679 --> 34:29.460
What are you doing?

34:29.480 --> 34:30.650
That's the heart flame!

34:30.679 --> 34:31.889
I can see it.

34:31.909 --> 34:32.949
Chong Zhao.

34:32.980 --> 34:34.250
Look.

34:34.280 --> 34:36.550
Maybe after Bai Shuo saved the Yi child,

34:36.570 --> 34:38.170
the heart flame sensed it and responded.

34:38.190 --> 34:39.270
That's nonsense!

34:40.120 --> 34:41.080
Maybe this human planned it

34:41.110 --> 34:42.530
with those Yi citizens from the start.

34:42.550 --> 34:44.810
How could she get the heart flame with just a pill?

34:45.800 --> 34:47.350
That's cheating.

34:47.389 --> 34:49.659
Cheating, cheating!

34:49.710 --> 34:50.929
That's the first heart flame.

34:50.960 --> 34:52.210
Whether it's taken by the Eternals

34:52.230 --> 34:53.350
or the demons,

34:53.400 --> 34:53.929
it can't

34:53.960 --> 34:54.770
be taken

34:54.790 --> 34:55.830
by a human!

34:55.880 --> 34:57.030
Exactly!

34:57.050 --> 34:58.420
Why can't a human

34:58.450 --> 35:00.450
have the heart flame?

35:03.320 --> 35:04.800
This Contest is for Eternals and demons.

35:04.830 --> 35:07.220
The Human Race doesn't even have the right to attend it!

35:07.450 --> 35:08.490
Is that so?

35:10.470 --> 35:12.140
I'm here in Yi City with her.

35:12.160 --> 35:13.600
That gives her the right!

35:15.330 --> 35:16.500
Not convinced?

35:17.130 --> 35:18.130
Come fight me.

35:19.810 --> 35:20.290
You...

35:20.320 --> 35:21.030
Senior.

35:21.270 --> 35:23.100
Why are you sticking up for her?

35:23.130 --> 35:24.220
Why?

35:24.510 --> 35:26.470
You just got to Yi City.

35:26.950 --> 35:29.360
Why are you already at each other's throats?

35:36.910 --> 35:38.280
I'm Wu Zhao.

35:38.300 --> 35:39.860
I'm the deputy general under King of Yi.

35:40.370 --> 35:42.240
Welcome to Yi City

35:42.660 --> 35:43.580
to attend

35:43.630 --> 35:44.630
the Wutong Martial Arts Contest.

35:44.630 --> 35:45.800
You've come at the right time.

35:46.400 --> 35:48.190
I've got one question.

35:48.330 --> 35:49.900
What gives her, a human,

35:49.930 --> 35:52.010
the right to take the heart flame?

35:52.040 --> 35:53.730
Before the Master of Bright Moon Palace came,

35:53.750 --> 35:55.230
he'd notified the King

35:55.840 --> 35:58.400
that a human would contend in the competition.

35:58.530 --> 35:59.850
The King gave his approval.

36:01.100 --> 36:02.370
Isn't that right,

36:02.560 --> 36:03.520
Master?

36:04.570 --> 36:06.360
-Master?
-Master?

36:06.820 --> 36:08.540
He's the Master of Bright Moon Palace?

36:09.010 --> 36:10.890
He's come to Yi City in person.

36:10.910 --> 36:12.140
We don't stand a chance.

36:14.290 --> 36:15.440
The Wutong Contest

36:16.130 --> 36:17.730
has already begun the moment

36:17.760 --> 36:18.950
you entered the city.

36:18.970 --> 36:20.270
There are three heart flames.

36:20.340 --> 36:21.610
The first gives rise to the second,

36:21.640 --> 36:23.120
the second to the third.

36:23.140 --> 36:24.350
The first two heart flames

36:24.370 --> 36:25.730
are naturally generated

36:26.220 --> 36:27.920
and choose their owners themselves.

36:28.070 --> 36:29.630
But the third heart flame

36:29.660 --> 36:30.750
must be kindled by the King

36:30.780 --> 36:32.100
along with the Eternals and demons

36:32.120 --> 36:33.600
by burning Wutong branches

36:33.630 --> 36:35.240
at the Fenlan Banquet.

36:35.660 --> 36:37.930
The one who collects all three heart flames

36:38.450 --> 36:40.760
will be the victor of the Wutong Contest

36:40.790 --> 36:42.620
and receive the Wutong Spirit Pill.

36:42.770 --> 36:45.120
This has been the rule for the past thousand years.

36:45.210 --> 36:46.410
I hope I've answered

36:46.440 --> 36:47.860
your question.

36:48.650 --> 36:49.850
The heart flame chooses its owner.

36:50.340 --> 36:51.380
No one can interfere.

36:53.060 --> 36:54.470
Magic is forbidden in Yi City.

36:54.490 --> 36:55.860
Eternals and demons are equals here.

36:55.890 --> 36:57.000
I wish

36:57.020 --> 36:58.290
you all

36:58.320 --> 36:59.760
a victorious start

36:59.780 --> 37:01.240
and an enjoyable return.

37:10.530 --> 37:11.470
Come up.

37:20.180 --> 37:20.890
Shuo.

37:24.740 --> 37:25.300
Chong Zhao.

37:25.320 --> 37:26.800
Let's settle down too.

37:27.670 --> 37:28.550
Okay.

37:29.480 --> 37:30.330
Brother,

37:30.360 --> 37:32.340
among the Three Kings of the Demon Race,

37:32.370 --> 37:34.430
the Master of Bright Moon Palace is the most powerful.

37:34.460 --> 37:35.860
What do you think we should do?

37:35.890 --> 37:37.140
If we don't show some goodwill,

37:37.160 --> 37:38.990
we may offend him.

37:39.020 --> 37:40.350
But if we do show goodwill,

37:40.370 --> 37:41.800
we may upset the heads of Jingyou Mountain

37:41.840 --> 37:43.320
and Cold Spring Palace.

37:43.750 --> 37:44.860
Let's stay neutral.

37:45.860 --> 37:46.970
The more neutral, the better.

37:47.000 --> 37:47.720
After all,

37:47.750 --> 37:49.110
we're here for the Contest,

37:49.150 --> 37:49.850
right?

37:49.870 --> 37:50.890
Yeah.

37:50.960 --> 37:51.760
We just

37:51.790 --> 37:52.580
won't ask questions

37:52.600 --> 37:53.480
or get involved.

37:54.110 --> 37:54.630
Right.

37:54.650 --> 37:55.820
No questions. No involvement.

37:56.080 --> 37:57.970
But why has the Master of Bright Moon Palace

37:57.990 --> 37:59.150
brought a human with him?

37:59.190 --> 38:00.810
What did I just say?

38:00.830 --> 38:02.060
No questions!

38:02.670 --> 38:04.080
Got it?

38:04.750 --> 38:05.390
Yes.

38:05.440 --> 38:06.460
No questions.

38:06.480 --> 38:07.580
No questions.

38:07.820 --> 38:08.660
Let's go.

38:09.040 --> 38:09.850
Go.

38:10.440 --> 38:11.360
Let's go.

38:14.230 --> 38:16.630
Don't you think everything

38:16.630 --> 38:18.110
is going a bit too smoothly?

38:18.590 --> 38:20.550
Eternals and demons just entered the city.

38:20.570 --> 38:22.220
Before they even got to grab a bite,

38:22.250 --> 38:23.680
a kid fell ill,

38:23.710 --> 38:25.920
and a bunch of Yi citizens rushed over, throwing accusations.

38:25.940 --> 38:27.690
It happened so fast,

38:27.880 --> 38:30.150
almost like someone planned it beforehand.

38:34.290 --> 38:35.330
Go on.

38:36.980 --> 38:38.580
Then I saved that kid

38:38.630 --> 38:40.640
and got the first heart flame.

38:40.670 --> 38:42.980
It's said the heart flame chooses its owner,

38:43.000 --> 38:44.750
but why do I feel like

38:44.960 --> 38:45.710
someone's intentionally

38:45.730 --> 38:47.500
given this heart flame to me?

38:48.110 --> 38:49.060
You've gotten smarter.

38:49.860 --> 38:52.120
What I want to hear isn't praise.

38:53.630 --> 38:55.610
Giving the first heart flame to you

38:56.120 --> 38:58.810
would make you the target of both Eternals and demons.

38:58.920 --> 39:00.840
Everyone will have their eyes on you.

39:00.860 --> 39:03.020
No matter who's pulling the strings behind the scenes,

39:03.080 --> 39:04.760
the game has already begun.

39:05.140 --> 39:06.100
And,

39:06.690 --> 39:08.370
it's more interesting than I expected.

39:09.250 --> 39:10.210
This isn't a conspiracy.

39:10.610 --> 39:11.480
It's a blatant scheme.

39:11.630 --> 39:12.510
Bai Shuo,

39:13.240 --> 39:14.990
they're coming for you.

39:15.630 --> 39:16.940
But to be exact,

39:18.020 --> 39:19.750
they're after the Desireless Stone.

39:20.330 --> 39:21.600
It's the Desireless Stone again.

39:22.700 --> 39:23.510
Looks like

39:23.510 --> 39:25.510
I'll have to turn defense into offense.

39:25.770 --> 39:27.080
If someone's targeting me,

39:27.410 --> 39:29.340
they'll definitely make moves behind my back.

39:32.320 --> 39:36.520
[Sihai Inn]

39:49.010 --> 39:51.660
I saved your life once.

39:51.680 --> 39:53.510
Is this how you treat someone who saved your life?

39:53.540 --> 39:55.210
You're a demon, and I'm an Eternal.

39:55.240 --> 39:57.060
We're on different paths.

39:57.080 --> 39:58.360
The truth about my parents' deaths,

39:58.360 --> 39:59.550
I'll find it out myself.

39:59.750 --> 40:00.990
If I worked with a demon

40:01.030 --> 40:02.340
to uncover the truth,

40:02.360 --> 40:04.980
my parents would turn in their graves!

40:10.660 --> 40:12.570
Chong Zhao,

40:12.600 --> 40:14.680
remember what you said today.

40:14.770 --> 40:15.560
From now on,

40:15.590 --> 40:16.430
whatever you want,

40:16.450 --> 40:17.860
I'll take it from you.

40:17.890 --> 40:18.960
You refuse to work with me.

40:18.980 --> 40:20.540
Then let's see how long you can hold out.

40:20.570 --> 40:21.380
Get out!

40:21.550 --> 40:22.840
Don't make me fight you.

40:24.340 --> 40:25.810
You're the one who should leave.

40:26.500 --> 40:27.700
What do you mean?

40:29.200 --> 40:30.890
Don't say I didn't warn you.

40:30.920 --> 40:32.320
Yi City is dangerous.

40:32.360 --> 40:34.420
Don't let those old fools from Lanling

40:34.440 --> 40:36.160
end up holding your funeral.

40:37.230 --> 40:38.270
Chong Zhao,

40:38.290 --> 40:39.290
it's me.

40:40.450 --> 40:41.470
Get out.

40:41.720 --> 40:42.560
What?

40:42.850 --> 40:43.730
Are you worried

40:43.760 --> 40:45.280
Bai Shuo will see me?

40:46.400 --> 40:47.440
Or

40:48.430 --> 40:50.590
are you afraid you won't be able to explain things to her?

40:50.630 --> 40:51.900
Get lost!

40:56.390 --> 40:57.540
What's that sound?

40:59.440 --> 41:00.600
A cat.

41:01.260 --> 41:02.060
Shuo.

41:02.920 --> 41:03.800
Have you changed your mind?

41:03.800 --> 41:04.920
You're willing to go back with me?

41:05.960 --> 41:07.320
I came to ask

41:07.320 --> 41:09.190
what happened to Old Turtle after I left.

41:09.960 --> 41:10.840
He's fine.

41:11.090 --> 41:12.070
He was just punished to make

41:12.070 --> 41:13.320
an extra hundred pills every month.

41:13.800 --> 41:14.880
Nothing else?

41:15.790 --> 41:16.680
No.

41:17.800 --> 41:18.920
I'm glad he's fine.

41:19.310 --> 41:20.020
Shuo.

41:23.210 --> 41:25.210
There's nothing else you want to say to me?

41:27.010 --> 41:28.130
What more

41:28.150 --> 41:29.770
can I say?

41:29.890 --> 41:31.020
I've said it before,

41:31.180 --> 41:32.500
we're no longer on the same path.

41:33.000 --> 41:34.560
If that's true,

41:35.370 --> 41:37.080
why did you speak up for me just now?

41:40.480 --> 41:41.920
We spent ten years together.

41:42.380 --> 41:43.880
To hide your identity,

41:43.900 --> 41:45.190
you always pretended to be weak.

41:46.040 --> 41:47.050
Helping you

41:47.080 --> 41:48.950
seems to have become a habit of mine.

41:49.480 --> 41:51.140
I forgot again just now.

41:51.280 --> 41:52.810
You're an Eternal from Lanling.

41:53.030 --> 41:54.760
You don't need me to stand up for you.

41:55.510 --> 41:56.000
Shuo.

41:56.000 --> 41:58.220
While I was in Lanling, I heard some things.

41:58.800 --> 42:01.150
I know you did all that back in Ning'an City to protect me,

42:01.670 --> 42:03.550
and I know you endured 300 lashes.

42:03.710 --> 42:04.880
But Chong Zhao,

42:05.590 --> 42:07.380
I can't thank you.

42:08.810 --> 42:09.700
Then,

42:11.230 --> 42:12.280
do you hate me?

42:14.280 --> 42:15.110
No.

42:16.330 --> 42:17.810
The demon poison wasn't your doing,

42:18.230 --> 42:20.020
nor did you cause my father's death.

42:20.940 --> 42:22.500
You were just wrong

42:22.520 --> 42:24.090
in taking my life too seriously.

42:25.220 --> 42:27.490
To protect me, you almost ruined a whole city.

42:27.740 --> 42:28.670
Have you ever thought

42:28.670 --> 42:30.040
even if I survived,

42:30.070 --> 42:31.360
how would I live with all of this

42:31.360 --> 42:32.500
after knowing the truth?

42:33.650 --> 42:35.240
It was all my fault.

42:35.730 --> 42:36.840
I was too confident,

42:36.880 --> 42:38.660
and the demons made use of it.

42:39.650 --> 42:40.480
I'm sorry.

42:41.450 --> 42:42.260
But I…

42:42.280 --> 42:43.320
I really didn't expect things

42:43.320 --> 42:44.860
to end up like that.

42:44.890 --> 42:46.830
I know you didn't mean it,

42:47.140 --> 42:49.010
so I don't want to blame you anymore.

42:49.880 --> 42:50.710
Can we

42:51.580 --> 42:53.600
go back to the way we used to be?

42:59.290 --> 43:02.620
♫That year, that year♫

43:01.850 --> 43:04.430
Everything in Ning'an City is over now.

43:03.100 --> 43:06.480
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

43:05.390 --> 43:07.390
You're no longer that steamed bun boy,

43:06.880 --> 43:10.440
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

43:08.570 --> 43:10.010
and I'm no longer that

43:10.600 --> 43:12.730
devil-may-care girl.

43:10.920 --> 43:13.950
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

43:14.570 --> 43:17.870
♫That year, that year♫

43:15.510 --> 43:17.430
I'll walk my own way.

43:18.250 --> 43:21.660
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

43:18.490 --> 43:19.450
You too.

43:21.690 --> 43:22.610
Shuo.

43:22.170 --> 43:25.530
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

43:24.880 --> 43:26.320
What about you and Fan Yue?

43:26.700 --> 43:29.130
♫Layer after layer♫

43:27.120 --> 43:28.120
What exactly…

43:29.880 --> 43:32.890
♫Another year passed♫

43:31.490 --> 43:33.530
is your relationship now?

43:33.560 --> 43:35.640
Both of us need the power of the Desireless Stone.

43:35.910 --> 43:37.070
It's just cooperation.

43:37.730 --> 43:40.740
♫Another year passed♫

43:37.900 --> 43:39.670
He's been protecting you.

43:39.700 --> 43:41.030
What he's been protecting

43:41.050 --> 43:42.400
is the Desireless Stone.

43:50.050 --> 43:51.530
You chatted for a long time.

43:54.370 --> 43:55.810
You're a Demon King,

43:55.830 --> 43:57.140
yet you eavesdrop?

43:58.210 --> 44:00.100
I wouldn't stoop to something like that.

44:00.530 --> 44:01.860
What you wanted to ask him

44:01.890 --> 44:03.080
and what you'd say,

44:03.100 --> 44:04.530
I don't need to listen to know.

44:06.620 --> 44:07.980
You think you know me very well?

44:10.630 --> 44:11.880
At least better than he does.

44:12.470 --> 44:13.700
Since you're on different paths,

44:13.720 --> 44:15.510
don't waste time on all this sentimentality.

44:17.210 --> 44:18.330
The night has fallen.

44:18.650 --> 44:20.480
It's time to explore the city.
